26:43.038 --> 26:44.480
out. I came home kind of disconsolate, having one 
probably pretty good plate. But I don't know. I

26:53.073 --> 26:54.375
didn't see anything in the hypo. So I didn't make a 
big deal of it and sort of got on with my life for a

26:54.415 --> 26:58.722
couple of days. After a few days, I said, oh, my. 
